$$
p_{flip} = \left\{
\begin{array}{lr}
1, & \mathrm{if}\, \Delta E \leq 0 \\
\mathrm{exp}\left(-\beta \Delta E\right), & \mathrm{if}\, \Delta E > 0 
\end{array}
\right. ,
$$
$$
\mathrm{where} \, \beta=\frac{1}{k_\mathrm{B}T} .
$$
